Modifications made in this redistribution include:

- Disabled remote "phone-home" behavior to keep the tool fully local:
  * removed a call to a remote draft-retrieval cloud function endpoint, and
  * changed the default draft domain from a remote host to localhost.
- Added a safe, additive draft-editing module (edit_existing_impl.py) that
  loads an existing draft as a copy and applies changes without mutating the
  original.
- Removed material not needed for local MCP editing: demonstration/example
  scripts, third-party integration samples, and a bundled third-party skill.
- Removed local configuration and virtual-environment files.
- Neutralized author-specific filesystem paths in bundled templates.

